## RyzenAdj (bundled binary)

  https://github.com/FlyGoat/RyzenAdj
  License: LGPL-3.0

The plugin ships a prebuilt `ryzenadj` binary at
`bin/linux-x64/ryzenadj` to set AMD APU power limits on stock SteamOS,
where `ryzenadj` isn't packaged and `/usr` is read-only. The binary is
LGPL-3.0; its full license text is preserved alongside it in
`bin/linux-x64/LICENSE-ryzenadj`, and `bin/linux-x64/SOURCE.txt` pins the
exact upstream tag and commit it was built from. `build-ryzenadj.sh`
reproduces the build. The binary dynamic-links system libraries
(libpci/libudev/libcap), so an end user can relink against a modified
ryzenadj per LGPL-3.0 §4. This plugin's own source is BSD-3-Clause.
